Class TextDocumentImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • document.TextDocumentImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TextDocument
    public class TextDocumentImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements TextDocument
    This class implements the TextDocument interface and uses the least common subsequence for diff and least substring for commonSubText.
